Masira ma biro mako joma thiro jochan


1  Enobed marach manade ni joma riere e kitanda ka paro timo timbe maricho! Gichiew ka piny yawore mondo gitim richogo, nikech ging’eyo ni gin gi teko mar timo kamano. 
2  Ka gidwaro lop ng’ato, to gikawo akawa gi thwon. To kata ka gidwaro udi, to mago bende gikawo akawa. Gimayo ji kata mana utegi kaachiel gi mwandugi, mi giwegi nono. 
3  Omiyo Ruoth Nyasaye wacho niya, “Achano kelo masira kuomu, kendo enochal lodi e ng’utu ma ok unyal gonyo. Ok unuchak uwuothi ka uchung’ tir, nikech kindeno nobednu kinde marach. 
4  Ka kindeno ochopo, to ji nogou ngero, ka wero wend ywak niya,

‘Otiekwa chuth!

Ruoth Nyasaye osekawo pinywa,

mi omiyo joma oketowa e tuech!’


5  Kuom mano, onge ng’ato kuomu ma biro yudo lowo chieng’ ma ipoge kendo ni Ruoth Nyasaye.”


6  Ji lwera, kawachona niya “Kik ilwerwa! We lwerowa gi weche ma kamago. Masira ma kamano ok bi makowa! 
7  Iparo ni okwong’ jo-Israel koso? Bende Ruoth Nyasaye dikechi, mi tim gik ma kamago adier? Donge en ema owuoyo maber gi joma timbegi ni kare?”


8  To Ruoth Nyasaye dwoko niya, “To donge un ema uselokoru wasik joga? Joma duogo gi kue kaa e lweny ka paro ni masira orumo, umayo lopegi. 
9  Uriembo mond joga e mier ma gihero, kendo gueth moa kuoma usemayo nyithindgi nyaka chieng’. 
10  Auru malo mondo udhi! Ka eri ok en kama onego uyuee. Ubiro rado gi masira. 
11  Aneno ni janabi ma ji ohero en mana ng’at ma lworore e kor gweng’, gi weche maag miriambo, kokoro ni ji ni gibiro yudo divai gi kong’o mang’eny.


12  “To un jo-Israel modong’ abiro chokou kanyakla mana ka rombe manie abila, kata ka kweth manie lek. Koko nogore e pinyu nikech ng’eny mar ji. 
13  Jal ma noyawnigi rangach ema nogolgi oko. Ginipusre e dhorangach, mi gitony. Ruodhgi, ma en Ruoth Nyasaye owuon, ema notelnigi ka giwuok.”

